commentBody:
@Barry Ancona

What a great idea! 
I completely agree that this lovely puzzle would shine as a Wednesday themeless.

@Steve 

Thanks for the tip. I tend to solve only the NYT xword because of doing all the other games as well (Wordle, Connections, Strands, Letter Boxed...) 
But I'll keep it in mind!

@Barry Ancona
I'm not an expert, but I think it would be very challenging to row a rowboat without oarlocks.

Canoeing, on the other hand, is another story. I got my canoeing badge in camp (what fun!) and you definitely don't need to secure your paddles for that!

